{"tid":2187681,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【教學】係CALIBRE用Google Mail形式無綫傳送eBook到KINDLE","createTime":"2020-09-03T19:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T12:38:13.000Z","uid":370972,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe2bf862ba9b21b100a03cc874b1a2a8c073097","tid":2187681,"uid":370972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T19:33:23.000Z","msg":"首先去AMAZON攞你有嘅資料。<br />\n1）LOG IN <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/mycd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fmycd%2F&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=347ec30c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/mycd/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zjcLgJ7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzjcLgJ7.png&h=50c69044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2）入「Preference」，撳「Personal Document Settings」<br />\n3）會見到你部KINDLE嘅EMAIL ADDRESS，待用。<br />\n4）預備一個GMAIL（我建議用一個新或者用來裝垃圾嘅EMAIL做依個工作，減低風險）<br />\n5）去「 Approved Personal Document E-mail List 」加入GMAIL地址。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6uasQT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6uasQT.png&h=e15814ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下步驟係係MACBOOK進行，我估係WINDOWS都係差唔多。<br />\n6） 去「偏好設定」，再去「電子郵件分享書本」<br />\n7）撳「加入電子郵件」，輸入係後先攞機KINDLE 電郵地址。<br />\n8）入你個GMAIL EMAIL同相關資料 <br />\n9）去「<a href=\"https://myaccount.google.com/lesssecureapps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyaccount.google.com%2Flesssecureapps&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=57376887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myaccount.google.com/lesssecureapps</a> 」LOG IN入你嘅GMAIL ACCOUNT，開啟「允許低安全程式」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YSAwWMr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSAwWMr.png&h=f38180c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10）再撳「測試電子郵件」，如果OK，就會寫「SUCCESSFULLY」，否則就寫大渣ERROR嘢。<br />\n11) 撳「儲存」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PHiyqEv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPHiyqEv.png&h=3f833f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他相關TASK就係「連線與分享」處理。"},{"pid":"3e1fbd67e97a5b2f4663865583cfc5975e8a02c2","tid":2187681,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:58:56.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6e62c64955adc3d2721a07678c9890bdd42ea7fe","tid":2187681,"uid":21644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T04:21:06.000Z","msg":"用 send to kindle desktop app 會唔會方便d?"},{"pid":"1f81698531292d26d6953e6de4d4efb246cebca2","tid":2187681,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:31:29.000Z","msg":"10）再撳「測試電子郵件」，如果OK，就會寫「SUCCESSFULLY」，否則就寫大渣ERROR嘢。<br />\n11) 撳「儲存」<br />\n<br />\n點入去 圖11 個畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係CARIBRE 5.11"},{"pid":"f3d5838ae39ce6fc39bf59c764534dab4104294c","tid":2187681,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f81698531292d26d6953e6de4d4efb246cebca2","tid":2187681,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:31:29.000Z","msg":"10）再撳「測試電子郵件」，如果OK，就會寫「SUCCESSFULLY」，否則就寫大渣ERROR嘢。<br />\n11) 撳「儲存」<br />\n<br />\n點入去 圖11 個畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係CARIBRE 5.11"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:38:13.000Z","msg":"已解決<br />\n<br />\n用gmail, send 唔到書去kindle<br />\n請問主機名稱 <a href=\"http://smtp.gmail.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsmtp.gmail.com&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=3f8af5f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">smtp.gmail.com</a><br />\n連接埠: 587<br />\n<br />\n有冇錯"}]}